</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_353" id="175v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_353_r1l21">Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Schultheıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_353_r1l22">Schultheıſſ ʒu vvırcʒburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_353_r1l23"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt beuor Hanns Schultheıſſ / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_353_r1l24">habt wıe eẅch Berman Jud fürbracht hab daʒ abraham <expan>gan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_353_r1l25">Jud . bey vns . ein haws da dıe ſeklin Jnnenſıcʒe <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kawffen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_353_r1l26">welle etc / das haben wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> den Judenrat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_353_r1l27">bey vns beſandt vnd mıt Jn <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / dıe haben vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_353_r1l28"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> daʒ Jn <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht wıſſend ſey ſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır den </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_354" id="176r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l1"><expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> abraham gans auch beſandt vnd mıt Jm dauon geredt der hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l2">vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / man tu Jm daran vnrecht vnd ſprıcht auch er beger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l3">des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> hawſes ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> nıht ʒuuerkawffen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_353" id="175v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Schultheiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, schultheiss zu Wirczburg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor. Hanns Schultheiss, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch Berman jud
                        fürbracht hab, daz Abraham <expan>Gan<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, jud bey uns, ein
                        haws, da die Seklin innensicze, <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kawffen</expan> welle
                        etc., das haben wir <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> den judenrat bey uns besandt und mit
                        in <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt, die haben uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz in
                            <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht wissend sey; so
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir den <pb facs="#facs_354" id="176r"/>
<expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Abraham Gans auch besandt und mit im
                        davon geredt, der hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, man tu im
                        daran unrecht und spricht auch, er beger des
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> hawses zu disen
                            <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht zu verkawffen.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
